Parameter(s):	DEPTH, sediment/rock [m] (Depth sed) * GEOCODE * PI: Moffa-Sanchez, Paola (https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1857-8954, paola.l.moffa-sanchez@durham.ac.uk) * COMMENT: Mid-depth
